Well, here it is. Another attempt to make an X-Man work.

Inspirationthis

.....


Let me get one thing out the way: Yes, I'm aware of the entire X-Man Syndrome that no doubt pops into your mind upon first glance of this article. That's sort've the point. I thoroughly enjoy Humanoid SCP's, or at least the ones done right. I think the idea of some of these humanoid SCPs trying to become 

My favorite film is Unbreakable. In particular, I love the implication that art more often imitates life than vice versa. I wanted to explore this with the Superman character concept and, hopefully, break the illusion of heroic vigilantism.




